  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You must have a token on the scene to use this spell (Warpgate mutation limitation).</p><p>You must have an actor called \"CPR - Healing Spirit\" in your actors directory. You can enable the \"Keep Summon Actors Updated\" setting to have this happen automatically.</p><p>The healing spirit will automatically have a template created around it that will prompt a friendly entering target to get healed.</p><p>After casting this spell a new feature called \"Healing Spirit - Move\" will be available in your features.</p><p>If you use \"Tidy 5e Sheet\" it will automatically be favorited.</p><p>If you use \"Custom Character Sheet Sections\" it will be in it's own section called \"Spell Features.\"</p><p>You can customize the avatars and tokens for this feature with custom file paths with the Medkit -&gt; Configure.</p><p><em>This spell is safe to be renamed.</em></p>",
